This paper discusses policy iteration methods for Markov decision problems, which are commonly studied in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of deep neural networks in reinforcement learning is also mentioned. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
